00:35:54.010 --> 00:35:59.753 align:middle line:84%
>>Effortlessly, right now, today
is incorporate healthy fats,

00:35:59.753 --> 00:36:06.650 align:middle line:84%
healthy proteins, cut down the
sugars, exercise, and shake,

00:36:06.650 --> 00:36:08.550 align:middle line:84%
and you will change
your ability to deal

00:36:08.550 --> 00:36:10.075 align:middle line:90%
with stress indefinitely.

00:36:10.075 --> 00:36:13.580 align:middle line:84%
If you did that every
day and nothing more,

00:36:13.580 --> 00:36:17.800 align:middle line:84%
you would be far healthier than
if you didn't do those things.

00:36:17.800 --> 00:36:22.210 align:middle line:84%
So now we know that to be
in our fight or flight state

00:36:22.210 --> 00:36:23.975 align:middle line:90%
all the time is detrimental.

00:36:23.975 --> 00:36:25.330 align:middle line:90%


00:36:25.330 --> 00:36:30.220 align:middle line:84%
And it does so at the expense
of our ability to be here.

00:36:30.220 --> 00:36:34.275 align:middle line:84%
And when we're home from work,
we would like to be here.

00:36:34.275 --> 00:36:36.180 align:middle line:90%
It would serve us best.

00:36:36.180 --> 00:36:38.270 align:middle line:84%
It would help regulate
those hormones,

00:36:38.270 --> 00:36:40.150 align:middle line:84%
help us enjoy life
a little bit more,

00:36:40.150 --> 00:36:44.760 align:middle line:84%
help us maybe be a little more
relatable to those we love,

00:36:44.760 --> 00:36:49.185 align:middle line:84%
and to find a lot more enjoyment
and presence in our day

00:36:49.185 --> 00:36:52.270 align:middle line:84%
to day that doesn't
require us going back

00:36:52.270 --> 00:36:54.910 align:middle line:84%
to an adrenalized state
to feel alive again.

00:36:54.910 --> 00:36:57.100 align:middle line:90%


00:36:57.100 --> 00:36:59.412 align:middle line:84%
So how do we do this
with mental entrainment?

00:36:59.412 --> 00:37:01.782 align:middle line:90%
Because food can do it.

00:37:01.782 --> 00:37:04.160 align:middle line:90%
Exercise can help.

00:37:04.160 --> 00:37:05.600 align:middle line:90%
Shaking can help.

00:37:05.600 --> 00:37:08.990 align:middle line:84%
And then mental entrainment
is the icing on cake.

00:37:08.990 --> 00:37:10.220 align:middle line:90%


00:37:10.220 --> 00:37:12.770 align:middle line:84%
Some of you may have experience
with mental entrainment

00:37:12.770 --> 00:37:16.940 align:middle line:84%
where you are
envisioning or rehearsing

00:37:16.940 --> 00:37:20.355 align:middle line:84%
a mental script of how a certain
procedure is going to go,

00:37:20.355 --> 00:37:23.380 align:middle line:84%
and you do that over
and over and over again

00:37:23.380 --> 00:37:26.170 align:middle line:84%
so that, eventually
over time, you

00:37:26.170 --> 00:37:30.219 align:middle line:84%
can react as though that
script had been practiced.

00:37:30.219 --> 00:37:31.520 align:middle line:90%


00:37:31.520 --> 00:37:36.050 align:middle line:84%
So you're working off a
script that you rehearsed

00:37:36.050 --> 00:37:39.600 align:middle line:84%
until it becomes an
effortless, retrievable action

00:37:39.600 --> 00:37:41.660 align:middle line:90%
or memory in your body.

00:37:41.660 --> 00:37:45.870 align:middle line:84%
This is how we get better
at use of firearms.

00:37:45.870 --> 00:37:48.840 align:middle line:84%
This is how we get better
at playing instruments,

00:37:48.840 --> 00:37:49.940 align:middle line:90%
at playing sports.

00:37:49.940 --> 00:37:51.080 align:middle line:90%


00:37:51.080 --> 00:37:54.970 align:middle line:84%
Any activity that we
want to get better at

00:37:54.970 --> 00:37:59.640 align:middle line:84%
requires us to create
and rehearse scripts.

00:37:59.640 --> 00:38:03.050 align:middle line:84%
Some of those are scripts in
the body, physical motions,

00:38:03.050 --> 00:38:04.880 align:middle line:84%
and some of those
are mental scripts.

00:38:04.880 --> 00:38:05.713 align:middle line:90%
